    avatar: 'O',
  },
  {
    name: 'Elena Rodriguez',
    role: 'VP Product, HealthSync',
    content:
      'Their UI/UX team worked seamlessly with the frontend engineers to deliver a pixel-perfect, native-feeling healthcare app in half the anticipated timeline. Truly impressive.',
